1.2.0
 - Updated help view
 - Improved flags handling
 - Snapper snapshots are now disabled by default (Enable them with -b flag)
 - Prioritize DNF5 over DNF4
 - Error out when script is not run as sudo

1.1.1
 - Changed snapper snapshot type to pre-post
 - Fix errors for PC without snapper

1.1.0
 - Added support for creating automatic snapshots with snapper
 - Fix not fetching packages with APT

1.0.0
 - Initial release
